{"tid":2013606,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"波斯尼亞從中國輸入無效呼吸機，疑涉及貪污","createTime":"2020-05-12T11:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T14:12:22.000Z","uid":75656,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"515802821fb1f5205ecb9f78e4a4daeb8f558cca","tid":2013606,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:42:43.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒疾病，COVID-19）全球蔓延，救治重症患者的呼吸機需求激增，南歐國家波士尼亞與赫塞哥維納（以下簡稱波赫）最近用公帑從中國購入近100部呼吸機，結果發現無效，且事件可能涉及貪汙。<br />\n<br />\n《美聯社》報導，負責採購約100部呼吸機的是一間鮮為人知的水果加工處理廠「銀樹莓」（Silver Raspberry），沒有進口醫療設備的許可，卻獲得高額500萬歐元（約新台幣1.6億元），引發外界質疑政府為何會將採購呼吸機，交由一間名不經傳的水果加工廠處理。據稱該公司與政治圈有關聯，檢察官已就貪污和詐騙展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n檢察官在一份聲明中指出，初步發現進口的呼吸機連治療武漢肺炎的基本功能也未能達到，因此不建議給重症患者使用。該公司老闆否認誇大呼吸機價格，聲稱他是利用與中國的業務關係，來完成「人道主義使命」。<br />\n<br />\n報導提到，貪汙在波赫不足為奇，根據2019年透明國際「清廉指數」排行榜，該國在180國中排名第101名。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3162594\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3162594&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmJj7jGrzIfagxCK2eNaONkM%3D&h=792db558\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3162594&h=7d6b36ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3162594</a><br />\n<br />\n美聯社:<a href=\"https://apnews.com/5363cf8ab0c788c0a6d7e25eb3577f09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2F5363cf8ab0c788c0a6d7e25eb3577f09&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmJj7jGrzIfagxCK2eNaONkM%3D&h=7270ae86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apnews.com/5363cf8ab0c788c0a6d7e25eb3577f09</a>"},{"pid":"a70cdb91c333e4631b4e73fe02806c1b986982c9","tid":2013606,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:44:09.000Z","msg":"又有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecab7a4ccb5d8a0efca396f46a7ba2cf3ae192ec